t claims Shwe provided over a half billion dollars per year to the regime i=
n the two years after the coup, helping fund a $1 billion spending spree fo=
r arms, including fighter jets, attack drones, assault helicopters, tank pa=
rts, and advanced missile systems.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The purc=
hases have enabled what the U.N. Special Rapporteur called =E2=80=9Cprobabl=
