theoretically possible=C2=A0answers:</p><ol style=3D"list-style-type: decim=
al; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px=
;">Sometimes, in investigating a company, Hunterbrook Media will find stuff=
