t kind of story? Doing business with bad people might be morally bad,=C2=A0=
but good for the bottom line. As a journalistic endeavor, Hunterbrook Media=
 might want to call attention to these abuses. As a profit-seeking hedge fu=
nd, Hunterbrook Capital might pass. (Posco International=E2=80=99s stock <e=
m>is</em> down this week.)</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Sometim=
es, in investigating a company, Hunterbrook Media=E2=80=99s journalists mig=
ht learn of wrongdoing from inside sources at the company, and might rely o=
