 solid; background-color: #ccc;">discussed Hunterbrook=E2=80=99s</a> first =
published investigation of a public company, I noted that it shorted the st=
ock, got long a competitor=E2=80=99s stock, filed some lawsuits and also fi=
led an SEC whistleblower complaint. =E2=80=9CIf you can find out bad news a=
bout companies, there are a lot of ways to make money,=E2=80=9D I wrote. Po=
